dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Portage County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Portage County, Wisconsin at 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Portage_Hydro_2016. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Portage_HydroLine_2016' and 'Portage_HydroPoly_2016'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.co.portage.wi.gov/375/Land-Information-GIS
